1. *Poslednjih* godinu dana su se puno promenili. (The last year has changed a lot.)
2. On je u *poslednjih* nekoliko meseci postao veoma uspešan. (He has become very successful in the last few months.)
3. *Poslednjih* dana su se svi trudili da postignu dobre rezultate. (Everyone has been trying to achieve good results in the last days.)
4. U *poslednjih* godinu dana su se promenili stavovi ljudi. (People's attitudes have changed in the last year.)
5. Ona je bila u *poslednjih* par godina veoma uspešna. (She has been very successful in the last few years.)